Gallery

Source: vignettes/gallery.Rmd

This section shows how to use the examples available in the github.com/d3/d3/wiki/Gallery gallery, the R examples can be found in github.com/rstudio/r2d3/tree/master/inst/samples.

Morley

bl.ocks.org/mbostock/4061502

library(r2d3)
r2d3(
  read.csv("morley.csv"),
  "morley.js",
  d3_version = 3,
  container = "div",
  dependencies = c("morley.css", "box.js")
  )
)

Bubbles

bl.ocks.org/mbostock/4063269

flares <- read.csv("flare.csv")
r2d3(
  flares[!is.na(flares$value), ],
  "bubbles.js",
  d3_version = 4
)

Bullets

bl.ocks.org/mbostock/4061961

r2d3(
  jsonlite::read_json("bullets.json"),
  "bullets.js",
  d3_version = 3,
  container = "div",
  dependencies = c("bullets.css", "helper.js"),
  height = 300
)

Calendar

bl.ocks.org/mbostock/4063318

r2d3(
  read.csv("dji.csv"),
  "calendar.js",
  d3_version = 4,
  container = "div",
  height = 1950
)

Cartogram

bl.ocks.org/mbostock/4055908

r2d3(
  jsonlite::read_json("us.json"),
  "cartogram.js",
  d3_version = 3,
  dependencies = c("cartogram.css", "topojson.min.js",
  height = 400
)

Chord

bl.ocks.org/mbostock/4062006

r2d3(
  matrix(
    c(
      11975,  5871, 8916, 2868,
      1951, 10048, 2060, 6171,
      8010, 16145, 8090, 8045,
      1013,   990,  940, 6907
    ),
    ncol = 4, nrow = 4, byrow = T
  ),
  "chord.js",
  d3_version = 4,
  dependencies = "chord.css"
)
